OL,3,CWoman admits role in Ely riots, that
OL,4,Cfollowed e-bike crash deaths
OL,6,FA woman has pleaded guilty to taking
OL,7,Fpart in the Ely riots, which broke out
OL,8,Ffollowing the death of two teenagers
OL,9,Fkilled in an electric bike collision.
OL,11,FKyrees Sullivan, 16, and Harvey Evans,
OL,12,F15, were killed on 22 May 2023, after
OL,13,Ftheir e-bike crashed in the Cardiff
OL,14,Fsuburb. After the boys' deaths, there
OL,15,Fwere hours of violence and vandalism
OL,16,Fwith around 150 people attending a
OL,17,Friot that saw missiles thrown at
OL,18,Fpolice.
