OL,3,CWoman admits role in Ely riots, that
OL,4,Cfollowed e-bike crash deaths
OL,6,FMichaela Gonzales, 37, of Plymouth
OL,7,FWood Close, Ely, was due to face trial
OL,8,Fat Newport Crown Court today but she
OL,9,Fchanged her plea to guilty to rioting
OL,10,Fbefore the case was opened.
OL,12,FA jury had been sworn in for the trial
OL,13,Fand formally found Gonzales guilty of
OL,14,Frioting.
OL,16,FThe defendant was remanded on bail and
OL,17,Fwill be sentenced on June 8.
OL,19,FA trial will proceed in respect of
OL,20,FAshdon O'Dare, 28, of Penygarn Road,
OL,21,FEly, who faces a count of rioting.
