OL,3,CWoman admits role in Ely riots, that
OL,4,Cfollowed e-bike crash deaths
OL,6,FBefore the crash, CCTV showed a police
OL,7,Fvan driving behind the teenagers. It
OL,8,Fwas approximately half a mile away
OL,9,Ffrom the e-bike, on a different road,
OL,10,Fwhen the fatal collision occurred.
OL,12,FIOPC director David Ford said: "Our
OL,13,Fthoughts and sympathies continue to be
OL,14,Fwith the families of Kyrees and Harvey
OL,15,Fand everyone affected by the loss of
OL,16,Fsuch young lives. We know the boys'
OL,17,Fdeaths have had a deep impact on the
OL,18,Flocal community.
