OL,6,F"Our role when someone dies following
OL,7,Fpolice contact is to examine all the
OL,8,Fcircumstances surrounding that
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,F"Our independent investigation looked
OL,12,Fat the interactions South Wales Police
OL,13,Fhad with the boys before the
OL,14,Fcollision, plus accounts provided by
OL,15,Fofficers at the scene and later to our
OL,16,Finvestigation.
